<item>
 <title>Empowering Iraqis With Disabilities</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/disabilitynation/~3/chBEMozEhMo/empowering-iraqis-disabilities</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Bruce Curtis is a for-real role model, using his years of living with his disability and his job with Berkeley's &lt;a href="http://www.wid.org"&gt;World Institute on Disability,&lt;/a&gt; to provide mobility training and adaptive devices to newly disabled people in war-torn Iraq. Even more than the challenges of an inaccessible environment, &lt;a href="http://www.insidebayarea.com/news/ci_11103490"&gt;Curtis told Oakland Tribune correspondent Barbara Grady&lt;/a&gt; that attitudes and not picturing a future for people with disabilities are the biggest barriers to success for Iraqis.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Curtis is a quadriplegic who trains disabled Iraqis in how to handle the daily challenges of their disabilities. He helps them with using wheelchairs and learning how to advocate for their rights in a country where the disabled have few opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.disabilitynation.net/blog/empowering-iraqis-disabilities"&gt;read more&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:7Q72WNTAKBA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?d=7Q72WNTAKBA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:V_sGLiPBpWU"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?i=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:qj6IDK7rITs"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:l6gmwiTKsz0"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?d=l6gmwiTKsz0" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?i=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:TzevzKxY174"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?d=TzevzKxY174" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:63t7Ie-LG7Y"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?d=63t7Ie-LG7Y" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?a=chBEMozEhMo:aqpFHs1TVi4:Jwdi1b3fU3Q"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/disabilitynation?d=Jwdi1b3fU3Q" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;