 <title>More Retailers Featuring People With Disabilities in Spots</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/disabilitynation/~3/p_UuR_ibPN4/more-retailers-featuring-people-disabilities-spots</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;With the holiday season upon us there are all kinds of new advertisements making the rounds. And, I've noticed a couple that prominently feature people with disabilities.&lt;/p&gt;

